<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Welcome to dfn!.</title>
  </head>

  <body style="margin:0; padding:0; background:#ffffff; font-family:Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color:#000;">

    <div style="max-width:560px; margin:72px auto; padding:0 24px;">

      <!-- Logo -->
      <div style="font-size:20px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:-0.02em;">
        dfn!.
      </div>

      <!-- Hero -->
      <h1 style="margin:56px 0 28px; font-size:44px; font-weight:600; line-height:1.05; letter-spacing:-0.03em;">
        Get paid before the shoot.
      </h1>

      <!-- Greeting -->
      <p style="margin:0 0 20px; font-size:18px; line-height:1.6;">
        Hey {{#if name}}{{name}}{{else}}there{{/if}},
      </p>

      <!-- Core Message -->
      <p style="margin:0 0 20px; font-size:18px; line-height:1.6;">
        You joined early — and that matters.
      </p>

      <p style="margin:0 0 20px; font-size:18px; line-height:1.6;">
        dfn!. was built from a simple frustration:
        talented creators doing great work,
        then waiting… and waiting… to get paid.
      </p>

      <p style="margin:0 0 20px; font-size:18px; line-height:1.6;">
        We’re changing that.
      </p>

      <p style="margin:0 0 36px; font-size:18px; line-height:1.6;">
        This is the beginning of a system designed to protect your time,
        your work, and your money.
      </p>

      {{#if verificationUrl}}
        <div style="margin-bottom:40px;">
          <a href="{{verificationUrl}}"
             style="display:inline-block;
                    background:#fff;
                    color:#000;
                    border:2px solid #000;
                    text-decoration:none;
                    padding:16px 28px;
                    font-size:15px;
                    font-weight:600;
                    border-radius:0;">
            Verify your email
          </a>
        </div>
      {{/if}}

      <!-- Startup Journey Section -->
      <div style="margin-top:48px; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6;">
        <p style="margin:0 0 16px;">
          Right now, define! is focused on one thing:
        </p>

        <p style="margin:0 0 16px; font-weight:600;">
          Securing payments before the work begins.
        </p>

        <p style="margin:0;">
          As we grow, we’ll build more layers on top of this foundation —
          but always with clarity, simplicity, and creator-first thinking.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Closing -->
      <div style="margin-top:64px; font-size:14px;">
        <p style="margin:0 0 8px;">
          Thank you for being here this early.
        </p>

        <p style="margin:0;">
          Let’s build something valuable.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top:40px; font-size:12px; color:#6b7280;">
        © {{year}} define!.
      </div>

    </div>

  </body>
</html>
